cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper proposes a framework that combines reinforcement learning, evolutionary algorithms, and imitation learning to solve continuous control tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves neural networks and optimization, which are related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
